pgpool-II: pgpool-II (Connection pooler for PostgreSQL)
pgpool-II:
pgpool-II: pgpool-II is a middleware that works between PostgreSQL servers and a
pgpool-II: PostgreSQL database client. It is licensed under BSD license. It
pgpool-II: provides the following features: Connection Pooling, Replication,
pgpool-II: Load Balance, Limiting Exceeding Connections and Parallel Query.
